{"tid":1211074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟立法會我哋而家爭幾多票？轉追擊建制派議員有冇得諗？","createTime":"2019-06-12T15:01:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T16:12:15.000Z","uid":87571,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"44f03dffdfe5f0f8d842e8da4901e41016e103ca","tid":1211074,"uid":87571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:01:23.000Z","msg":"而家睇個款林鄭月娥一定唔會撤回今次條例。搞到咁大單野又開晒槍，有冇可能令某啲建制派議員轉呔？<br />\n<br />\n我諗有某啲議員我哋可以嘗試追擊或者說服，例如自由黨嘅議員，田北晨，新民黨嘅議員等等。<br />\n<br />\n上次23條都係靠田北俊轉呔，唔係靠政府撤回條例<br />\n<br />\n究竟有冇得諗？"},{"pid":"57984bedffc7833d0e05dfe69dc75b21dc5b7579","tid":1211074,"uid":87571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:02:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c443a7f7baf12a91a281780eddf537134cfb0836","tid":1211074,"uid":87571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:03:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c9bc771e3e8f5221d992fe6f029ff9919ac5eec","tid":1211074,"uid":52939,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:05:28.000Z","msg":"說服無可能<br />\n佢地都要同阿爺交代<br />\n反而令佢地入唔到去投票<br />\n反而有用<br />\n<br />\n佢地可能心入面都唔想投。搵個借口唔投"},{"pid":"5519f58d67caabba1d580d83245943fc84e16688","tid":1211074,"uid":87571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:07:00.000Z","msg":"究竟爭幾多票先過唔到？"},{"pid":"fdbc6935af22ea116b10fbb51dca11555b4edaa4","tid":1211074,"uid":54884,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:07:34.000Z","msg":"只要自由黨同經民聯唔支持就得"},{"pid":"d7afc7efb2ff913b293378c80c45347fb10b8ab8","tid":1211074,"uid":87571,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"fdbc6935af22ea116b10fbb51dca11555b4edaa4","tid":1211074,"uid":54884,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:07:34.000Z","msg":"只要自由黨同經民聯唔支持就得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:11:57.000Z","msg":"石禮謙<br />\n鐘國斌<br />\n田北辰<br />\n<br />\n呢幾個唔係冇可能convince 到"},{"pid":"9d05958aa34d95726ef70dc43d46aa1ed763228c","tid":1211074,"uid":35592,"l